* When posting or replying via gopher:
  * Your deletion password will be "password" (but your IP address must match!)
  * You can start your post with "!Name" to use a name other than Anonymous, up
    to 16 characters
  * You can start your post (after your "!Name" if you include one) with a URL
    (starting with "http" or "https") to an image < 1 MiB in order to upload it
